featured_reviews.review_id:
A peaceful environment to pray five times a day. Please note Zuhar Namaz time is 2:30 PM.

Wuzu Khana on ground and first floor & Faltered drinking water also available on ground floor. Please make sure that you visiting the mosque before 15 minutes.

Don't forget to offer the Farz Namaz five times a day. Allah give us the blessings to complete our life according to ISLAM & on the way of Hazrat Muhammad Mustafa S.A.W.
